        which lie close to the median halo mass-concentration relation
        predicted in ΛCDM. The inferred total mass,
        M<sub>200</sub><sup>total</sup>=1.08<sub>-0.14</sub><sup>+0.20</sup> ×
        10<sup>12</sup> M<sub>⊙</sub>, is in good agreement with recent
