        effect of galaxy formation on subhalo populations in two state-
        of-the-art sets of hydrodynamical Λcold
        dark matter (ΛCDM) simulations of Milky Way
        mass haloes, APOSTLE and AURIGA. We introduce a new method for
        tracking the orbits of subhaloes between simulation snapshots
